Package data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client
    Client WebSocket class used to talk with the server
    EntityData
    Abstract class that acts as a model for the entities/actors in the game.
    GameData
    GameData stores information pertaining to entities in the game for sending/recieving from the server.
    HitData
    Contains information about a projectile's collision with a player.
    JsonHeader
    Abstract class which contains the the protocol for sending Json messages.
    PlayerData
    Data class that encapsulates relevant player data to be sent to the server and other players.
    ProjectileData
    Data class that encapsulates relevant projectile data to be sent to the server and other players.
    Ship
    Class which contains relevant ship information for a player.
    UserQueryData
    Simple class to encapsulate user queries.
